room_title: Escape room "303 Coulrophobia Ln." by Escape the Place in Orange County
room_address: 26469 Rancho Pkwy S Lake Forest, CA 92630
room_description: Pets have been mysteriously disappearing in your neighborhood. All of them have yet to be found despite ongoing searches. Reports have been made to local authorities for months resulting in nothing but dead ends. Your beloved family pet is now one of the missing. Rumors and suspicion point to the creepy house on the corner. You and your friends decide to take action and confront the neighbor. What you find is truly more sinister than you imagined...
